🩸 Monqez

Monqez is a smart, community-driven platform that connects blood donors with hospitals and blood banks based on real-time needs. Instead of relying on traditional or unorganized donation methods, Monqez provides a fast, reliable, and efficient way to match donors with urgent cases.

The platform aims to reduce emergency response time, improve coordination between medical entities and donors, and ultimately save lives. It is a purposeful project that addresses the problem of delayed or inaccessible blood donation systems.

